PrecisAppointment of Marc A. Brault as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of South Africa; Peter Hancock as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Turkey; Archibald McArthur as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Colombia with concurrent accreditation as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Ecuador; James Fox as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Guatemala; Simon Wade as High Commissioner for Canada to the Cooperative Republic of Guyana; Mark Entwistle as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Cuba; Brian Dickson as Ambassador and Permanent Representative of Canada to the Organization of American States; and Leonard Legault as Ambassador of Canada to the Holy See.
